author: Associated Press
title: Australian Police Raid Cruise Ship Linked to 600 Coronavirus Cases and 15 Deaths
description: Police boarded a the Ruby Princess cruise ship to seize evidence linked to hundreds of coronavirus infections and 15 deaths across Australia.
content:
(SYDNEY) — Police wearing protective gear boarded a cruise ship to seize evidence and question crew members of the vessel linked to hundreds of coronavirus infections and 15 deaths across Australia.
About 2,700 passengers disembarked from the ship on March 1… [+1515 chars]
